      description="With a combination of education as a web developer and a keen eye for design and UI/UX, I create growth and enable myself to work wholeheartedly with frontend development. In this way, I strengthen the brand's position as being the best when it comes to frontend development, while simultaneously creating valuable results that ultimately lead to better sales-ready leads."
    />
    <Projects />
